ill running, the QLHV group is running, the Agent Status cron is running despite its history of aborts, and the DTLX Telegram group remains failed. Orphans are still orphans.\\n\\nThe only meaningful change here is that Lead direct session reactivating — the 5p crons spinning up child sessions for QLHV work is just normal operational activity. So the pipeline status is still DEGRADED because of that persistent DTLX Telegram failure, but everything else checks out with all the MCPs running and the 5p crons doing their job.\\n\\nNow I'm trying to figure out if I actually need to send this report to the QLHV group. Looking at the task instructions, it says to send a concise change report, but the DTLX-specific cron is only supposed to send when there are changes — and the only change here is that Lead direct went from idle to running, which is the kind of internal reactivation that doesn't necessarily warrant notifying the QLHV group. The QLHV report format is pretty clear—it should only cover actual changes. The Lead direct session reactivating is an internal state change that doesn't fit that criteria, and the QLHV child sessions spawning is just normal 5p monitor behavior. Looking back at the previous reports, I can see they were triggered by more substantial events like failures, recoveries, or new session spawns—not routine state fluctuations. Since there's nothing genuinely new to report here, staying silent is the right call. Looking at the other crons in the system, they're all running normally—the agent status and both monitor sessions are cycling as expected. The orphans are still there from before, but nothing new has triggered a report, so I'm staying silent this cycle.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Comparing current state (03:48 UTC) against `heartbeat-state.json` (03:22 UTC):\\n\\n**Active sessions now:**\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p) ✅ still running — 5p monitor doing its normal cycle\\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p) ✅ still running — this cron\\n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status) ✅ still running — normal cycle\\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` ✅ still running — Lead's active work (same task, unchanged from 03:43)\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ still running — QLHV child sessions, same\\n\\n**Unchanged from 03:22:**\\n- DTLX Telegram group still FAILED (known pre-existing)\\n- Orphans still present (ac986a8d, b653a6c0)\\n- Pipeline DEGRADED status unchanged\\n\\nNo new events. No new failures. No new spawns or deaths. **Stable.**\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 435,\n            \"output\": 1064,\n            \"totalTokens\": 42655,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14264,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 26892,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776224977714,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e3dd217307446525fab9a30b0a688\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"2fc0a9e2\",\n            \"seq\": 7\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5163901258\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776224777880,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 105955,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"star